Package: wickraverify
Type: Package
Title: Verify Any Backtest
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-verify over its C ABI hub: create a Verifier,
    recompute a claimed backtest report with the deterministic Wickra engine and
    confirm or refute it field by field - the same protocol as the CLI and every
    other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-verify
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-verify/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-verify C ABI shared library (WKVERIFY_LIB) and its
    header (WKVERIFY_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
